{"tid":2364977,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"指公務員財政壓力大　兩工會去信陳茂波　要求額外寬免薪俸稅","createTime":"2021-01-13T11:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T13:42:30.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"a9a38c690728c3235b846a2db03ae800e6283efd","tid":2364977,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"疫情下不少打工仔「手停口停」，失業率、就業不足率持續高企，不少人期望當局在下月底公布的《財政預算案》中「派糖」紓困，當中更包括公務員。<br />\n<br />\n《立場新聞》取得政府紀律部隊人員總工會、公務員總工會聯署，昨日（12 日）寫予財政司司長陳茂波的信件，要求額外寬免薪俸稅。信中形容公務員未受惠於政府抗疫基金，加上不少基層公務員的家庭成員被裁，面臨財政壓力。兩工會認為寬免措施有助刺激公務員消費，達到「振軍心、助經濟」。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，政府紀律部隊人員總工會轄下盟會包括消防、懲教、海關及入境不同職級人員共 11 個工會；公務員總工會轄下盟會則有不同政府部門、職級人員合共 58 個工會。"},{"pid":"f861d4de60c8c23c120f0a646eb265542df36690","tid":2364977,"uid":182222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:40:14.000Z","msg":"你話笑死唔笑死<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a8e62c16b03f05231f651dbb5dbf379da190fc7","tid":2364977,"uid":125380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:40:42.000Z","msg":"兩工會認為寬免措施有助刺激公務員消費，達到「振軍心、助經濟」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26cce02b583dd90be9f4b69e28907b5a42d8d125","tid":2364977,"uid":173271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:42:52.000Z","msg":"不打自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95bf83d14876553c29855d46be2e59f5b9aae547","tid":2364977,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T11:44:13.000Z","msg":"其實連登班基層公務員唔洗交好多稅<br />\n<br />\n